OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772016033
OL,3,CDriverless car firm Wayve bags #1.1bn
OL,4,Cinvestment to help launch on UK roads
OL,6,FWayve, the self-driving car firm set
OL,7,Fto launch robotaxis on UK roads, has
OL,8,Fraised 1.5 billion US dollars (#1.1
OL,9,Fbillion) from investors including
OL,10,FUber, Microsoft and chip giant Nvidia.
OL,12,FIt has secured 1.2 billion dollars
OL,13,F(#890 million) through a funding round
OL,14,Fbacked by the major tech firms,
OL,15,Finstitutional investors and car
OL,16,Fmakers, with Uber investing extra
OL,17,Ffunds to help deliver its driverless
OL,18,Ftaxi plans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
