OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772016033
OL,3,CDriverless car firm Wayve bags #1.1bn
OL,4,Cinvestment to help launch on UK roads
OL,6,FThe Series D funding round, which is
OL,7,Fone of the largest ever for a British
OL,8,Fstart-up, values the London-based
OL,9,Fbusiness at around 8.6 billion dollars
OL,10,F(#6.4 billion).
OL,12,FMajor car manufacturers Mercedes-Benz,
OL,13,FNissan and Stellantis have also
OL,14,Finjected cash as part of the deal.
OL,16,FIt comes as Wayve prepares to launch
OL,17,Frobotaxis in London later this year as
OL,18,Fpart of a partnership with ride-
OL,19,Fhailing platform Uber.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772016033
OL,3,CDriverless car firm Wayve bags #1.1bn
OL,4,Cinvestment to help launch on UK roads
OL,6,FWayve said it will launch the
OL,7,Fcommercial robotaxi trials in the city
OL,8,Fin 2026 with ambitions to deploy its
OL,9,F"supervised autonomy software" in
OL,10,Fconsumer vehicles from 2027.
OL,12,FThe company's technology used
OL,13,Fartificial intelligence models which
OL,14,Flearn how to drive using video
OL,15,Fcontent, driving data and recognising
OL,16,Fpatterns.
OL,18,FUS rival Waymo has also revealed plans
OL,19,Fto make its driverless private hire
OL,20,Fvehicles available in London from next
OL,21,Fyear.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
