FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772016033
OL,3,CDriverless car firm Wayve bags #1.1bn
OL,4,Cinvestment to help launch on UK roads
OL,6,FWayve's fresh funding round was led by
OL,7,Finvestors Eclipse, Balderton and
OL,8,FSoftBank Vision Fund 2, and also saw
OL,9,Fnew investment from Ontario Teachers'
OL,10,FPension Plan, Baillie Gifford, British
OL,11,FBusiness Bank, Icehouse Ventures,
OL,12,FSchroders Capital and other
OL,13,Finstitutional investors.
OL,15,FBosses said the investment will
OL,16,Faccelerate Wayve's plans to launch its
OL,17,Ftechnology into commercial vehicles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772016033
OL,3,CDriverless car firm Wayve bags #1.1bn
OL,4,Cinvestment to help launch on UK roads
OL,6,FAlex Kendall, co-founder and chief
OL,7,Fexecutive of Wayve, said: "With 1.5
OL,8,Fbillion dollars secured, we are
OL,9,Fbuilding for a total addressable
OL,10,Fmarket that spans every vehicle that
OL,11,Fmoves.
OL,13,F"Autonomy will not scale through city-
OL,14,Fby-city robotaxi deployments alone.
OL,16,F"It will scale through a trusted
OL,17,Fplatform that automakers and fleets
OL,18,Fcan deploy globally and improve
OL,19,Fcontinuously."
OL,26,@oD@[OUuD@AOUxD@AOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
