OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772016033
OL,3,CDriverless car firm Wayve bags #1.1bn
OL,4,Cinvestment to help launch on UK roads
OL,6,FUber chief executive Dara Khosrowshahi
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are very proud to continue
OL,8,Fto deepen our partnership with Wayve,
OL,9,Fwith plans to deploy together in more
OL,10,Fthan 10 markets around the world.
OL,12,F"Wayve's powerful end-to-end approach
OL,13,Fis purpose-built for scale, safety and
OL,14,Feffectiveness, and we're excited to
OL,15,Fwork with them across multiple OEMs
OL,16,F(original equipment manufacturers) and
OL,17,Fgeographies, which we'll share more
OL,18,Fabout soon."
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOUzD@LO]
