OL,3,CDriverless car firm Wayve bags #1.1bn
OL,4,Cinvestment to help launch on UK roads
OL,6,FTechnology Secretary Liz Kendall said:
OL,7,F"Wayve is a powerful example of the
OL,8,Fstrength, ambition and potential of
OL,9,FBritain's innovative firms.
OL,11,F"This fund raise demonstrates the
OL,12,Finternational confidence in our
OL,13,Fbrilliant AI sector and reaffirms
OL,14,FBritain's position as the leading
OL,15,Fscale-up ecosystem in Europe.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
